casebody.data:
CLEVELAND METRO. BAR ASSN.
v.
AUSTIN 2018-0159 Supreme Court of Ohio. October 1, 2018

CASE ANNOUNCEMENTS

DISCIPLINARY CASES

On respondent's motion for leave to answer the certification of default. Motion granted. Matter remanded to the board for further proceedings under Gov.Bar R. V(12). The interim default suspension imposed against respondent on February 23, 2018, shall remain in place while this matter is pending before the board. Proceedings before this court in this case are stayed until further order of this court.
